@page
@model WebApplicatieWebdev.Pages.DeveloperProfileModel
@{
	ViewData["Title"] = "Developer Profile";
}
<partial name="_CookieConsentPartial" />

<div class="d-flex flex-column">
	<div class="p-2">
		<h4>Skills</h4>
		<ul>
			<li>HTML</li>
			<li>CSS</li>
			<li>JavaScript</li>
			<li>Java</li>
			<li>C#</li>
			<li>C++</li>
			<li>Python</li>
			<li>AngularJS</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="p-2">
		<h4>Description</h4>
		<p>
			As an experienced developer, I have honed my skills in programming and software development over the years. I have either pursued formal education in computer science or have learned through practical experience and self-study.
			I would describe myself as an analytical, detail-oriented, and persistent problem solver. I enjoy working both independently and as part of a team, and I am able to communicate technical information in a clear and concise manner.
			My expertise includes proficiency in multiple programming languages, databases, and software development tools, and I am always eager to learn and adapt to new technologies and platforms. Additionally, I have experience in project management and software testing, as well as an understanding of software development methodologies such as Agile or Waterfall.
			Overall, I take pride in being a highly skilled and dedicated professional who plays a critical role in creating the software and technology that powers our world today.
		</p>
	</div>
    <div id="imageCarousel" class="p-2 carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-bs-target="#imageCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-bs-target="#imageCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-bs-target="#imageCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="2"></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="img/carouselImage1.jpg" alt="First slide">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="img/carouselImage2.jpeg" alt="Second slide">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img class="d-block w-100" src="img/carouselImage3.jpg" alt="Third slide">
            </div>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#imageCarousel" role="button" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#imageCarousel" role="button" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
    </div>
</div>